Gravity-Condition-FoodInsecurity-1.name: Gravity_Condition_FoodInsecurity_1
Gravity-Condition-FoodInsecurity-1.description: This profile supports Gravity Project data elements that focus on the Food Insecurity domain. The profile constrains Conditions related to: Food insecurity, Mild food insecurity, Moderate food insecurity, or Severe food insecurity.

Gravity-Observation-FoodInsecurity-1.name: Gravity_Observation_FoodInsecurity_1
Gravity-Observation-FoodInsecurity-1.description: This profile supports Gravity Project data elements that focus on the Food Insecurity domain. The profile constrains Observations related to: Food insecurity. It allows the creation of Observations of: Food insecurity unknown, Food insecurity absent (aka Food security present), Food insecurity present, Mild food insecurity present, Moderate food insecurity present, and Severe food insecurity present.

Gravity-Goal-FoodInsecurity-1.name: Gravity_Goal_FoodInsecurity_1
Gravity-Goal-FoodInsecurity-1.description: This profile supports Gravity Project data elements that focus on the Food Insecurity domain. The profile constrains Goals related to: Food Security.
